              "id": "IC_kwDOFcwZ1c6Rp0eG",
              "body": "### PR summary [c3e6b8f9b3](https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/18377/commits/c3e6b8f9b3a2b8c7d847a6bf6f7c93396c29540f)\n\n#### Import changes for modified files\n\nNo significant changes to the import graph\n\n\n<details><summary>Import changes for all files</summary>\n\n|Files|Import difference|\n|-|-|\n| `Mathlib.Topology.Algebra.ClopenNhdofOne`|1000|\n\n</details>\n\n---\n\n<details><summary>\n\n#### Declarations diff\n\n</summary>\n\n`+ TopologicalAddGroup.addNegClosureNhd`\n`+ TopologicalGroup.mulInvClosureNhd`\n`+ existOpenNormalSubgroupSubClopenNhdsOfOne`\n`+ existOpenSubgroupSubClopenNhdsOfOne`\n`+ exist_mul_closure_nhd`\n`+ exists_mulInvClosureNhd`\n<details>\n  <summary>You can run this locally as follows</summary>\n\n\n```bash\n## summary with just the declaration names:\n./scripts/declarations_diff.sh <optional_commit>\n\n## more verbose report:\n./scripts/declarations_diff.sh long <optional_commit>\n```\n</details>\n\nThe doc-module for `script/declarations_diff.sh` contains some details about this script.\n\n</details>",
              "createdAt": "2024-10-29T09:16:04Z",
